videos.description: Gary Clark steals the inbound pass and finds teammate Jacob Evans for the slam.
videos.headline: Cincinnati's Clark finds Jacob Evans for the dunk

videos.description: Cincinnati guard Troy Caupain puts the Bearcats up by 19 just before halftime.
videos.headline: Bearcats' Caupain gets the tough layup to fall before halftime

videos.description: Troy Caupain finds Gary Clark in transition for the huge slam.
videos.headline: Cincinnati's Clark throws down the big alley-oop

videos.description: Dedric Lawson slams it down for Memphis to bring the Tigers within nine.
videos.headline: Memphis' Lawson slams it home for two

videos.description: Jeremiah Martin gets the tough layup plus the foul to pull the Tigers to within seven.
videos.headline: Memphis' Martin closes the gap to seven with the and-1

videos.description: Bearcats guard Jarron Cumberland throws down the putback dunk to seal the victory for Cincinnati.
videos.headline: Cincinnati's Cumberland with the big putback jam

videos.description: Four of No. 15 Cincinnati's starters record double-digit points in an 87-74 win against Memphis.
videos.headline: Cincinnati picks up 25th victory of season
